            <p style={{ fontSize: '12.5px', color: '#555', margin: '0 0 14px', lineHeight: 1.5, fontFamily: "'HubotSans', sans-serif" }}>
              Subscribe to be first to hear about bulk discounts, new products, and seasonal offers.
