              <p style={{ fontSize: '11px', color: '#888', margin: '0 0 10px', lineHeight: 1.5, fontFamily: "'HubotSans', sans-serif" }}>PDF, PNG, AI, PSD, EPS ΓÇö max 25MB. We'll review before printing.</p>
